This is a file encryption and decryption program.  Place both encrypt.java and decrypt.java in the same directory.

This program will encrypt .txt files containing only the following characters:

a-z
A-Z
0-9
?	
(
)
*
,
-
.
/
:
;
Space
!		

To encrypt the file 'MyFile.txt', on command line enter the following:
java encrypt MyFile.txt

This will create the file 'encrypted-MyFile.txt' in the same directory.

To decrypt on the command line enter the following:
java decrypt encrypted-MyFile.txt

You will be prompted to enter the decryption key.  Only the correct key will produce a readable file.  This will produce the file 'decrypted-encrypted-MyFile.txt'.

Enjoy!